flowchart LR
  %% System hardware block diagram, draw.io compatible

  MCU[RA6M5 微控制器]

  ETH_PHY[Ethernet PHY LAN8720A]
  RJ45[RJ45 以太网接口]
  WIFI[WiFi模块 W800]

  CANFD[CAN-FD收发链路]
  EL05_ARM[EL05 关节电机组 4x]
  EL05_GRIP[EL05 夹爪电机 1x]

  LCD[显示屏 ST7796S]
  TOUCH[触摸 FT5x06]
  MIC[数字麦克风 INMP441]

  FLASH[外部Flash W25Q64]
  LOGUART[串口日志接口]
  HOST[上位机/监控终端]

  MCU -->|RMII| ETH_PHY --> RJ45 --> HOST
  MCU -->|UART SCI6| WIFI --> HOST

  MCU -->|CANFD0| CANFD --> EL05_ARM
  CANFD --> EL05_GRIP

  MCU -->|SPI1| LCD
  MCU -->|I2C IIC2| TOUCH
  MCU -->|I2S SSI0 + GPT| MIC

  MCU -->|QSPI0| FLASH
  MCU -->|UART SCI7| LOGUART
